            <div class="title">
                Clause 1â€”(Provision For Her Royal Highness The Princess Elizabeth)
            </div>

            <div class="right-arrow">
                    <a href="/Commons/1948-01-27/debates/c594c561-79c0-466a-8cdd-ea01cacaa50e/Clause2%E2%80%94(ProvisionForHisRoyalHighnessTheDukeOfEdinburgh)" class="next" title="Go to the next debate">
